This list comprises a selection of some premiere and other recordings by musicians who have become closely associated with Alkan&#x27;s works. A comprehensive discography is available at the Alkan Society website.
* Piano Trio, Op. 30 – played by Trio Alkan. Recorded 1992. Naxos, 8555352 (2001)
