<doc id="439672" wikidata="Q3846759" url="?curid=439672" title="Ixhuatlán del Café">
<text>Ixhuatlán del Café is a city in the Mexican state of Veracruz. It serves as the municipal seat of the municipality of the same name.

The municipality covers a total surface area of 134.07 km2 and, in the 2000 census, reported a population of 19,945.
It is located at .

Its chief products are corn, coffee and fruits.

